{{> header}}
<h1>Verify Your Email Address</h1>

<p>Thank you for registering with {{appName}}! To ensure the security of your account and access all features, please verify your email address using the code below:</p>

<div class="otp-container">
    <div class="otp-code">{{otp}}</div>
    <p style="margin: 16px 0 0 0; font-size: 14px; color: #6B7280;">
        This code will expire in <span class="highlight">{{expiryMinutes}} minutes</span>
    </p>
</div>

<div style="background: #F0FDF4; border: 1px solid #DCFCE7; border-radius: 8px; padding: 16px; margin: 24px 0;">
    <p style="color: #166534; margin: 0; font-size: 14px;">
        <strong>Quick Tip:</strong> For the best experience, please verify your email address before exploring our platform.
    </p>
</div>

<p>If you did not create an account with {{appName}}, you can safely ignore this email.</p>

<p style="margin-top: 32px;">Best regards,<br><strong style="color: #1E40AF;">The {{appName}} Team</strong></p>
{{> footer}}